					<br /><br /><span class="profile_header">Child Profile</span><br /><p>Mathew is a 13-year-old boy who enjoys spending time in a family setting. Mathew achieves well academically in school, and he has several friends. Mathew loves to play video games! Mathew also enjoys helping to care for his foster family's dog. <br /><br />Mathew would like to join a family that is active and enjoys sports. Mathew would like to have siblings in his forever home, and he would love to have an extended family. Mathew is hopeful to find a home with pets, preferably dogs and fish. Mathew would like to have the ability to maintain contact with people that have been significant in his life, including members of his birth and foster families. Mathew would prosper in a family that understands trauma and is open to helping him engage in services that will help him continue to prosper. <br /><br />For more information contact Maria Leadon at 513-887-4355.</p><br /><br /></p>
				
				